# pmi-api configuration moved to the platform-root single source of truth:
#   /Users/reid/micah/pmi_data_platform/.env
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer; pmi-api's pydantic-settings probes
# all three of: cwd `.env`, this service-root `.env` (legacy), and the
# platform-root `pmi_data_platform/.env` (current).
#
# pmi-api specifically reads the following keys (prefixed `PMI_API_`):
#   - PMI_API_REQUIRE_AUTH
#   - PMI_API_CORS_ORIGINS
#   - PMI_API_PORT
# Plus everything pmi-core needs (PMI_DB_*, PMI_MLFLOW_*, PMI_LOG_LEVEL).
#
# Bootstrap a fresh checkout:
#   cp pmi_data_platform/.env.example pmi_data_platform/.env
